CS||cp||AT|^B@2^Y@35. If no side suits are shown (and against no-trump Slams in particular) tend to make the safest lead possible. This is doubly true if you have a considerable smattering of high cards. In such cases lay back and hope Declarer must come to you or possibly misguess the hand.|
